iplexers are designed to be used as outputs. The\ninverse design approach that allows for the implementation of more than six\noutput channels together with the proposed functionalities can help develop\ncompact and manufacturable 2D 1xN couplers.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 27 Feb 2019 09:29:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-02-28"}
