d of preserving backward\ncompatibility with the preceding variants on the scheduling procedure is\nexamined and discussed. Thanks to the execution time of the algorithm, which is\nless than one second, the network parameters like the frame length and cycle\nduration are explored to find their best choice concerning the schedule\nfeasibility.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 27 Feb 2019 12:51:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-02-28"}
